This topic describes how to install and configure Altoros Elasticsearch for PCF.

##<a id='install'></a> Install and Configure Altoros Elasticsearch for PCF

1. Download the product file from Pivotal Network.

1. Navigate to the Ops Manager Installation Dashboard and click **Import a Product** to upload the product file.

1. Under the **Import a Product** button, click **+** next to the version number of Altoros Elasticsearch for PCF.
This adds the tile to your staging area.

1. Click the newly added **Altoros Elasticsearch for PCF** tile.

1. Set up the network for tile:
  <%= image_tag("images/network.png") %>

1. Chose the BOSH stemcell version, compatible with Elasticsearch:
  <%= image_tag("images/stemcell.png") %>

1. Click **Save**.

1. Return to the Ops Manager Installation Dashboard and click **Apply Changes** to install the Altoros Elasticsearch for PCF tile.


